Uktar 12: I fear my contamination is growing worse. I see symbols of Mitra's
	wrath everywhere I look. I hear voices in rooms where no one else is.
	I can see things out of the corner of my eye that vanish when I try
	to look at them directly. I have drawn upon the Well of Life to
	sustain me, and its power is helping me deal with my problems. I
	don't understand why all these things are going wrong. If I was
	this flawed before, how could I have become a priestess, let alone
	be chosen to lead this church? I must be absolutely pure, as the
	slightest fault could bring down the doom I see suspended over me.
	I have sequestered myself in my quarters, for I find I can better
	deal with my temper and my lusts and my envy when I am not among
	other people.

